                 <GlobeIcon className="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" /> Strategic Analysis Dossier
               </h3>
               <div className="bg-slate-900/60 p-2 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 w-full md:w-64 h-48 md:h-auto">
